<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ش ظ ف<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٢٨٢٦ - ش ظ ف]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>شظُفَ يَشظُف، شَظَفًا وشَظافةً، فهو شَظِف وشَظيف<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• شظُف العيشُ:</span> ضاق واشتدّ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• شظُف الخُلُقُ:</span> ساء.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">• شظُف الشّجرُ:</span> يبِس لقلَّة الرَّيّ <span class="c1">"شحَّ ماءُ العيون فشظُف شجرُ الواحة-<span class="c5"> عودٌ شظِف:</span> يابس متكسِّر"</span>.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>